OL,3,C'On the mend': Tai Woffinden shares
OL,4,Cfirst message since crash
OL,6,FSpeedway star Tai Woffinden says he is
OL,7,F"on the mend" after a crash which left
OL,8,Fhim in a medically induced coma.
OL,10,FIn a social media post the 34-year-
OL,11,Fold, who races for the Sheffield
OL,12,FTigers, shared a picture from his
OL,13,Fhospital bed and thanked fans for
OL,14,Ftheir support.
OL,16,FHe said: "Turns out my injuries and an
OL,17,Finduced coma ain't no joke.
