OL,3,C'On the mend': Tai Woffinden shares
OL,4,Cfirst message since crash
OL,6,F"Im on the mend, but please bear with
OL,7,Fme for now. I just need a little more
OL,8,Ftime to rest and gather my thoughts.
OL,9,FI'll update you all later on in the
OL,10,Fweek.
OL,12,F"Please know how much i appreciate
OL,13,Feveryone's love and support from all
OL,14,Fover the world."
OL,16,FThe three-time Grand Prix world
OL,17,Fchampion, who is originally from
OL,18,FScunthorpe, was involved in a
OL,19,Fcollision with a teammate during a
OL,20,Frace in Poland on 30 March.
