OL,3,C'On the mend': Tai Woffinden shares
OL,4,Cfirst message since crash
OL,6,FHe suffered multiple fractures and a
OL,7,Fchest injury, and was taken by
OL,8,Fhelicopter to hospital where he was
OL,9,Fplaced in a medically induced coma on
OL,10,Fa ventilator.
OL,12,FFollowing the crash Woffinden's wife,
OL,13,FFaye, flew out from their home in
OL,14,FAustralia on Monday to be by his
OL,15,Fbedside.
OL,17,FShe later thanked those who had played
OL,18,Fa role in his recovery, but admitted
OL,19,Fit was an "incredibly difficult time".
